posts.post_title: FS: Lenox (Doyle) and Carolina Brights (Strang) PSA
posts.post_content:
I've got 2 rare back t-206's for sale:

1: Joe Doyle (Ny Giants) portrait with a Lenox back (black writing)
    PSA 2 

2. Sam Strang (Baltimore) with a Carolina Brights Back
    PSA 1.5 


    Asking $1,950.00 for the pair (net to me) price includes shipping within the contiguous USA.

    I apologize for lack of pics (having trouble with it) but if you will Pm me with your email address and any questions, I will be happy to answer and send them.

    I've completed deals with Brian Weisner, T-206fox (tony), Frank Burkett and several others during my first 18 months in the hobby.

    Thank you,
      Josh
